  "2026-06-19T11:23:29.559Z",codex-cli-agent,"Evidence: reopened exact regression lineage for GitHub Nightly Validation run 27816467001. Failure was macOS Node 20/extension-command.spec.ts expecting raw /var file URL while resolveNpmPackSpec returned canonical /private/var. Fixed helper test by realpathing the temp root after mkdtemp. Targeted test passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extensions/extension-command.spec.ts (94 tests). Repo gates passed after fix: pnpm quality:static, pnpm typecheck, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage = 100/100/100/100 (230 files, 4653 tests)."
